description:
Birk's Bible Stumpers
Play the computer or a friend answering questions from either the Old Testament or the New Testament. (You can even create your own questions!) 

Games: 20 Questions, Birk 500 and Power Slam 2000

************************************************************************************

Players: One or two
Language: English
Operating System (Tested On): Windows 98, ME, XP

************************************************************************************

Tips:
When you start the game you can skip the intro by clicking on the spinning computer. To end the game click on the &quot;Stop&quot; sign.

